topic.title: What is your favorite video game?
topic.body:
Tell me all about your favorite video game.
My favorite is Diablo 2. I like it because there's always something more to do. Killing Baal isn't beating the game, you know?

topic.title: Welcome!
topic.body:
Hello! I'm new here, but I thought that I could help to contribute to this place by creating this subverse where people could post topics about whatever.
The key to success for places like this are conversations and content. Since this isn't a content-based platform we'll need to make conversation.

Please leave a comment and maybe post something and I'll try to reply soonish (24-48 hours or so, I know this place is kind of slow.)

Why don't we start by sharing what you like about ZeroNet?
I like that it's uncensorable and that it's not reliant on a hosting service. This means that you can say what you want and be assured that if other people want to, they'll be able to read what you post.

What do you like about ZeroNet?
